member_experience_collection.title: Head of Digital Design
member_experience_collection.description:
As co founder of this visual communication agency in Spain, we produced innovative and high quality digital content for the Architecture and Engineering environments. From concept through production to final delivery, we specialised in innovative solutions to our clients needs and demands. I enjoyed this challenging and varied ecosystem where I sharpened my design and production skills, project management and client facing skills. During this time I have mastered the production pipeline in 3D Animation and Motion Graphics, as well as the art of delivering on our promises and motivating our team to resolve all the problems along the way.

Our Main Clients during this time where:
Mercedes-Benz AMG, Oracle/BMW USA17, Endesa WindPower, EcoBuild, British Research Establishment, Airbus Military, Comeen.

StudioLab Eu produces the very best & cutting edge images, videos and mobile apps applied to Architecture and CleanTech.

We are passionate about communication and the interconnection that the internet provides. Social networks and the accelerated development of new devices and platforms means that the marketing and communication ecosystem is constantly changing and moving forward. Daunting as it may seem, future generations of your end user will be adapted to this rapidly changing environment, will you?

Here at StudioLab we like to be one step ahead and take pride in investing heavily on emerging technologies and trends that can be of benefit for our clients and their future audience. We work hard to keep abreast, so you don’t have to!

member_experience_collection.company_name: Publicis Groupe - Saatchi & Saatchi - London HQ
member_experience_collection.description: Working as a senior consultant with this IT resourcing company that serviced the Publicis Group in the UK with support to their creative teams.

member_experience_collection.title: Production Analyst
member_experience_collection.description: This was a short contract where I was specifically called to cover for staff holidays. This time it was in the award winning play station games developing studios in London.

member_experience_collection.title: Senior Technical Creative Consultant
member_experience_collection.description: This company serves a variety of small studios and has undergone in the past 4 months the rebuilding of the entire facility. Creative support to the studio was mainly on In Design, Photoshop, Illustrator and Quark. Performed rollout of Adobe Creative Suite to designers and gave them training.

member_experience_collection.title: Senior Technical Creative Consultant
member_experience_collection.description: This was a short and sharp contract to rationalise the Apple Mac infrastructure of this leading advertising company in their Farringdon offices.

member_experience_collection.title: Systems and Media Consultant - Start Ups
member_experience_collection.description: In these months I provided consultancy, analysis and implementation for various startup design and media companies. This work encompassed from advising my clients on the best IT solutions for their businesses to implementing such recommendations. In these short contracts I helped web design agencies, photography studios, graphic design and furniture design start ups. This was a rewarding experience where I managed to ease my self back to a professional environment after taking a sabbatical. I also got back in touch with the latest industry developments and the new technologies important to my work.

member_experience_collection.title: Head of Digital Design
member_experience_collection.description:
As co founder of this visual communication agency in Spain, we produced innovative and high quality digital content for the Architecture and Engineering environments. From concept through production to final delivery, we specialised in innovative solutions to our clients needs and demands. I enjoyed this challenging and varied ecosystem where I sharpened my design and production skills, project management and client facing skills. During this time I have mastered the production pipeline in 3D Animation and Motion Graphics, as well as the art of delivering on our promises and motivating our team to resolve all the problems along the way.

Our Main Clients during this time where:
Mercedes-Benz AMG, Oracle/BMW USA17, Endesa WindPower, EcoBuild, British Research Establishment, Airbus Military, Comeen.

StudioLab Eu produces the very best & cutting edge images, videos and mobile apps applied to Architecture and CleanTech.

We are passionate about communication and the interconnection that the internet provides. Social networks and the accelerated development of new devices and platforms means that the marketing and communication ecosystem is constantly changing and moving forward. Daunting as it may seem, future generations of your end user will be adapted to this rapidly changing environment, will you?

Here at StudioLab we like to be one step ahead and take pride in investing heavily on emerging technologies and trends that can be of benefit for our clients and their future audience. We work hard to keep abreast, so you don’t have to!
